    "attributes": {
        "action": "Free criminal record check, to check trade workers that work in domestic homes.",
        "additional_details": "I believe that by giving the customer choice to research the criminal record of a tradesperson, free of charge,  will give the customer piece of mind that the trades personnel that they have accepted to do a job is not a risk to that household.",
        "background": "Grant the customer to a free criminal record check on trades personnel that they are thinking of giving business to.  This will give customers piece of mind that the trades personnel that are doing their work is not a known criminal.",
